title: 2 Br In-law Convenience & walking distance to SFSU/CCSF
posting_body: ['1 Large and 1 Medium Clean bright bedrooms with mirror closets, laminate floor, sliding glass door access to backyard', 'Living room/Kitchen with granite counter top, Sink, Refrigerator, Microware,  etc.', 'Bathroom wall and floor with tiles', 'Washer/Dryer, Separate entrance, street parking', 'Closed to everything: Whole Food, restaurants, 24hr fitness, schools, Stonestown shopping mall, freeway 101/280, Bart/Buses etc.', 'Walking distance to SFSU and CCSF', 'Utilities share with upstairs tenants', 'This unit for 2 people max', 'SFSU and CCSF students welcome', 'Request: No pet, no smoke, no drug, no loud party and no eviction history', '1st month rent, $2500 security deposit - 1-year lease', 'Total move in cost $4695 - Must be willing to provide ID/driver license, paystubs, bank statements/Proof of income; $35 credit check/each person.', 'Provide a brief information about yourself and your roommate', '樓下 乾淨, 安靜 1大房', '和 1 中 房 出租，$2195 一個月, 保证金 $2500，独立入口，浴室, 客廳 帶廚房有冰箱, 微波炉.', '有 洗衣, 干衣机,', '水电垃圾费另外按人头平分- 签约一年，可随时入住', '交通購物方便，步行距離 SFSU and CCSF, 超级市场, 购物, 餐厅, 健身房 24Hr, 巴士站和 Bart＆280 公路全靠近', '适合 2 大学生，无烟，无酒，无宠物，无派对，爱干净', '歡迎不吸煙 國際學生']
